<div class="show-details row">
	<div class="left-side col-lg-7">
		<div class="main-details h-auto py-4">
			<p class="card-text fw-medium m-0">Owned by: <i></i></p>
			<h4 class="card-title m-0 pb-1">
				Room in <%= listing.location %>, <%= listing.country %>
			</h4>
			<h6 class="main-amenities">
				<span class="capacity">5 </span> guests ·
				<span class="bedrooms">5 </span> bedrooms ·
				<span class="beds">5 </span> beds ·
				<span class="bathrooms">5 </span> bathrooms
			</h6>
			<div class="reviews-overview">
				<b><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> 4.95 </b> <b class="dot">· </b>
				<b class="total-reviews text-decoration-underline">20 reviews</b>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="host-overview d-flex gap-4 py-4 border-top border-bottom">
			<img
				src="../icon/Naruto.jpg"
				alt="host-dp"
				class="rounded-circle h-25 host-overview-dp"
			/>
			<div class="host-overview-info">
				<p class="host-name m-0">Hosted by <%= listing.owner.username %></p>
				<p class="host-expnc m-0 text-secondary">
					Superhost <span class="dot text-secondary">·</span> 12 years hosting
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="main-amenities py-4 d-flex flex-column gap-4 border-bottom">
			<div class="first-amnt d-flex gap-4">
				<div class="firepit amnt-svg"></div>
				<div class="amnt-info">
					<p class="head-amnt-info m-0">Outdoor entertainment</p>
					<p class="sub-amnt-info m-0 text-secondary">
						The firepit, alfresco dining, BBQ area and outdoor seating are great
						for summer trips
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="second-amnt d-flex gap-4">
				<div class="locMarker amnt-svg"></div>
				<div class="amnt-info">
					<p class="head-amnt-info m-0">Peace and quiet</p>
					<p class="sub-amnt-info m-0 text-secondary">
						Guests say this home is in a quiet area.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="third-amnt d-flex gap-4">
				<div class="calendar amnt-svg"></div>
				<div class="amnt-info">
					<p class="head-amnt-info m-0">Free cancellation before 30 Jun</p>
					<p class="sub-amnt-info m-0 text-secondary">
						Get a full refund if you change your mind.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="show-desc py-4 border-bottom">
			<p class="s-desc">
				The treehouse is nestled in the Himalayan subtropical pine forests. It
				is made keeping in mind to provide a comfortable and memorable stay to
				travelers seeking a break from the hustle of city life. <br />
				The house is cozy both in winter and summer. It has a 360-degree view of
				the greater Himalayas The treehouse is nestled in the Himalayan
				subtropical pine forests. It is made keeping in mind to provide a
				comfortable and memorable stay to travelers seeking a break from the
				hustle of city life. The house is cozy both in winter and summer. It has
				a 360-degree view of the greater Himalayas The treehouse is nestled in
				the Himalayan subtropical pine forests. It is made keeping in mind to
				provide a comfortable and memorable stay to travelers seeking a break
				from the hustle of city life. The house is cozy both in winter and
				summer. It has a 360-degree view of the greater Himalayas
			</p>
			<a
				class="icon-link link-underline-dark"
				href="#description-modal"
				data-bs-toggle="modal"
				data-bs-target="#description-modal"
			>
				<span class="show-f-desc">Show more</span>
				<span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
			</a>
		</div>
		<!-- 
		<div class="place-offers py-4">
			<h4 class="pb-2 s-title">What this place offers</h4>
			<ul>
				<%# listing.amenities.forEach(amenity => { %>
				<li><%# amenity %></li>
				<%# }); %>
			</ul>
		</div> -->

		<% if (currUser && currUser._id.equals(listing.owner._id)) { %>
		<div class="btns d-flex mt-4">
			<a href="/listings/<%= listing._id %>/edit" class="btn btn-dark">Edit</a>
			<form action="/listings/<%= listing._id %>?_method=DELETE" method="post">
				<button class="btn btn-danger offset-3">Delete</button>
			</form>
		</div>
		<% } %>
	</div>
	<div class="right-side col-lg-4">
		<p class="price pt-2">
			&#8377;&nbsp;<%= listing.price.toLocaleString("en-IN") %><span>
				night</span
			>
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
